OL,3,C'Walking on eggshells': Charities
OL,4,Cforecast rise in domestic abuse over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FA victim of domestic abuse has told
OL,8,FITV News West Country her perpetrator
OL,9,Fled to her having a distorted view of
OL,10,Freality and she had spent her life
OL,11,F"walking on eggshells".
OL,13,FIt comes as some charities are
OL,14,Fexpecting a rise of calls by nearly
OL,15,F50% over Christmas.
OL,17,FThey say the festive period is a
OL,18,F"pressure cooker" with financial
OL,19,Fworries and people spending more time
OL,20,Fat home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
