OL,3,C'Walking on eggshells': Charities
OL,4,Cforecast rise in domestic abuse over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FThe victim, who we've chosen not to
OL,8,Fname, said: "I was so anxious, like
OL,9,Fquite a lot, that I ended up becoming
OL,10,Fvery ill.
OL,12,F"What happened to me was all of the
OL,13,Flittle blocks would be removed over
OL,14,Ftime by little bits of devaluation,
OL,15,Flike criticism until you feel unstable.
OL,17,F"Then they will pretend to be the
OL,18,Fscaffolding to hold up your tower.
OL,19,FThey will pretend they are the only
OL,20,Fperson who is there for you.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
