OL,3,C'Walking on eggshells': Charities
OL,4,Cforecast rise in domestic abuse over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"These people isolate you, make you
OL,8,Ffeel not like yourself, plant seeds
OL,9,Fwith others to make you seem like the
OL,10,Fcrazy person and the problem.
OL,12,F"You need to start rebuilding,
OL,13,Fbreaking away from it, you can't
OL,14,Fmanage it in anyway apart from just
OL,15,Fget free and get help."
OL,17,FSociety Without Abuse (SWA), a
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse charity based in
OL,19,FSwindon, runs a programme called
OL,20,FOpen2Chance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
