OL,3,C'Walking on eggshells': Charities
OL,4,Cforecast rise in domestic abuse over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FIt is aimed at perpetrators, to
OL,8,Fprovide early intervention to support
OL,9,Fthose who want to change their
OL,10,F"harmful behaviours in relationships".
OL,12,FThe scheme saw a rise of 47% after
OL,13,Flast Christmas.
OL,15,FThe charity say they also see a peak
OL,16,Fin the number of calls of people
OL,17,Fasking for help over the festive
OL,18,Fperiod, which escalates when children
OL,19,Fgo back to school.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
