OL,3,C'Walking on eggshells': Charities
OL,4,Cforecast rise in domestic abuse over
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,F"Sometimes when children go back to
OL,8,Feducational settings we will see an
OL,9,Fincrease of people asking for help
OL,10,Fbecause the children will disclose
OL,11,Fwhat's been going on at home.
OL,13,F"It destroy's people's self esteem and
OL,14,Ftheir confidence in themselves."
OL,16,FAccording to the NSPCC nearly 70% of
OL,17,Fpeople know a child who might be
OL,18,Fexposed to domestic violence.
